					"value": "- Load up GustavDev/SCL_Main_A\r\n- Solve the Colony Vault puzzle. Let's be honest, you're not going to. But if you want to: \"goto 737 13 -110\" and interact with the mind flayer console.\r\n- Alternatively, just use \"oe COL_Vault_AutoSolve\" and the puzzle will solve itself and teleport you into place."
